Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:19.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Woke up with yawning,\Nit's dawning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:22.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:27.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Turned on my radio\NTo start up new day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:30.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As goddamed D.J. chattered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:32.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:39.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing news got over\NOn that air wave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NLove is rationed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:45.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NAcross the nation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:49.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight\NLove reflects world wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:50.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Almost another day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:55.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's a shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.29,0:01:01.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good-night, good-night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:06.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's a shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:10.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:16.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NLove is rationed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:19.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NAcross the nation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:23.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight\NLove reflects world wide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:24.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Almost another day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:28.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See you some other day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:37.10,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,KARAKURA STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:44.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, it's me… I've just arrived…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:49.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… Yeah, is that so?\NI ate dinner before I came…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:19.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're too late!\NThis is Karakura 3790!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:21.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We found the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:22.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to capture it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:34.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:37.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:43.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've failed to capture the target!\NOne of us is injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:46.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Send the Med Crew immediately!\NIt's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:58.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world\Nare they planning…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:05.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:09.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop repeating the same thing\Nto yourself…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:12.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m getting so irritated!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:15.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it on the news this morning…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:19.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,People from all over\Nhave gone missing…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:20.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That means…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:26.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those monsters they let loose\Nmight be attacking people…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:28.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:35.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, Lirin and the others' sensors\Ndidn’t catch anything either…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:40.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are those Bounts hiding…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:41.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:45.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Has any information come\Nfrom Soul Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:50.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Stealth Force seems to be here,\Nbut I haven't received any information…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we can't do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:56.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,until we find the Bounts\Nand those creatures…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:58.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:03.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Urahara is making\Na powerful sensor at my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:06.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Until it's finished, we're just going\Nto have to take our chances
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:10.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,at coming across them in the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will Ishida be all right…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:19.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He seemed really shocked\Nabout Yoshino…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:22.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He stayed silent even when\NI talked to him…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:25.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit worried…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:33.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:37.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's fallen in love with\Nthat Bount woman, huh? Gosh…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:41.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of him…!\NThat's not very considerate…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:42.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:45.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk about\Nbeing considerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:48.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:52.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really. Why are you two\Nalways like this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time to be\Nquarreling among friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:01.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Several hundreds of years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:04.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we lost many friends in\Nthis underground capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:10.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am especially moved that\Nwe will begin our final plan here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:12.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Though it is an ambitious plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:18.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the spite of our fallen allies\Nwill give us unlimited power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:23.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Soul Society\Nhas made their move,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:24.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:28.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The mineral here eliminates\Nall Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:34.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our newly born dolls also contain\Nlarge amounts of that mineral as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:39.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take the time to\Nrefresh ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:41.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,there are a few who don't know\Nthe results of my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:45.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bitto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:56.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They suck out the souls of living humans\Nand bring them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:06:00.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is a doll that was created\Nfrom Ugaki and my technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:04.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh… That's what you were doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:09.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we ended up trading\Nthe life of one of our friends, though…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:15.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But how is that different from us\Ndirectly sucking people's souls?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:19.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can't just be that there's no danger…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The souls that Bitto bring\Nare of high purity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:26.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words\Nthey're concentrated…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We shall begin sucking souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:33.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a practice that was considered taboo\Nby our tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:36.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That energy will be gradually\Nstored up in our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:42.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With this, our abilities should leap to\Nmore than ten times our current level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:43.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:44.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:48.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,More than ten times…\NIs that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:51.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. This is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:56.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With this power,\Nwe will fulfill our long-cherished wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:06:59.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Burn this into your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:06.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The moment that our tribe's laws\Nand history change!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have no feelings of pain\Nor regret…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:08:00.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All I feel is joy and power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:08.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… The collected souls are\Nconcentrated within the Bitto's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:10.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought it would produce\Nthis much power…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:12.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's not too bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:16.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass… Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mabashi…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:21.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not planning to do\Nthat as well? Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:24.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you’ve chickened out?\NYou baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:26.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:29.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking what you think about\Nbreaking our tribe's laws!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Sawatari…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mabashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:41.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Long ago, you sucked\Nmany living souls…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:45.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite long ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:50.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The side effects! That's why\Nyou've aged so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:53.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it was a taboo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:57.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying! It doesn't matter\Nif it means we gain power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if we're going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:00.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:09.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not say things that'll ruin\NKariya's historical moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:13.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:15.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The laws are one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:16.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but things like this are…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:17.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Mabashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:25.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are always controversies\Nin the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:28.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong\Nwith asserting your opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:00.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:04.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mabashi, the next time\Nyou accuse me of something,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:06.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you do it at the risk of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:09.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can say whatever\Nyou want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:23.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I am the law\Nof the Bount tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:32.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Stealth Force…was defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't have…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:38.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not all of them, but a few have…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:41.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that their stomachs were\Npierced by those monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:45.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, the monsters\Nthat the Bounts released
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:48.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,removed living human souls\Nand escaped…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:53.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel… The way they do things\Nisn't beautiful…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya,\Nwhat are they planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:11:00.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering information is\Nthe job of the Stealth Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the World of the Living?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:08.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You four will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:11.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have already spoken\Nto the Captains' committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:13.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:17.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A monster has appeared.\NThat's our specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:19.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it isn't a Hollow…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then our targets are those monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No. We're targeting the Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:26.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:27.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:31.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty messy work, isn't it…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:37.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the other lieutenants,\NI don't like ugly things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I chosen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:42.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I asked Zaraki,\Nhe said you had the most free time…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing. Is that so…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:52.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have the feeling that they're planning\Nsomething even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:56.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave it to just\NIchigo Kurosaki and Abarai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:57.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:11:58.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:04.86,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,URAHARA'S SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:14.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not bad\Nfor last minute preparations…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:16.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful, store owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:18.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:22.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry for interrupting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:23.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is a message from\NMadam Yoruichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:32.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I will be investigating in\NSoul Society for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:36.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful of the Bounts' movements”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:40.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… So how are things\Non the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:45.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Various posts are gathering information\Non the Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But they’re still uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:51.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will excuse myself now…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:59.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have to return to\NMadam Yoruichi immediately…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:05.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:06.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:11.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that Madam Yoruichi\Nlived in a rundown shack like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:19.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down… I'm sorry…\NBut it's pretty comfortable here…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep in mind that if something happens\Nto Madam Yoruichi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:25.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you won't get away easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:29.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, my…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:33.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to avoid being chased\Nby the Punishment Force…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:35.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ururu! Jinta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it's late, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:40.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could you go out for me for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:41.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:45.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But to call this place a rundown shack…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:53.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:57.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should go in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:59.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It would be bad if you were targeted…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:05.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, are you all right?\NYou look pale…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:09.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right… Urahara is calling you…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:10.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m counting on all of you tonight\Nas well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all split up and be\Non the look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:24.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who is fighting a monster
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:26.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,should exhibit\Nelevated Spiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:30.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will they really come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:34.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will happen if they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty tricky now…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:40.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why are you two like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting Orihime is the duty\Nof the Hikoboshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who would be me, Kurodo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:47.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be of any help in a fight\Nas a stuffed animal…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous for her to go\Nby herself…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:52.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!\NThen I'll go into a gigai as well…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lirin, that's enough! We're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:13.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh… What is this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:24.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:27.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than I imagined, Kariya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:29.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:35.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I feel as if I've become younger\Nby a hundred years, easily…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:38.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:40.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this is a doll I created,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:44.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,this is definitely a great achievement
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:47.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that marks the coming of\Na new age for Bounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:49.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is still just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:52.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we continue to absorb this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:56.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,an even more wonderful world\Nwill open itself for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:58.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is addictive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:01.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think I shall have some more…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:05.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this was worth taking\Nthe effort to research…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:09.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mabashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:16.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NThere's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:24.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Master Kariya, will you allow me\Nto treat his wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:30.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be cured… in an instant…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop! Let go! I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:37.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bitto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:39.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:57.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:59.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing to be afraid of…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:12.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Mabashi, to the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:22.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lirin, any sign of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:25.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all…\NI wonder what's going on…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:29.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can't Urahara finish that\Nsensor already…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I give up…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been curious about it, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What kinds of things do Sado\Nand Noba talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:45.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when they're alone together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:46.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably,\N“What should we have for dinner?”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:52.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or “The weather is nice today.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:53.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, maybe something like,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:58.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“It's delicious if you top\Nyour ramen with chocolate.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:00.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That would be you…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:01.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:05.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine them having\Na conversation…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:09.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do they even talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:19.41,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,CONVERSATION FAILED
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:23.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo that bastard…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:25.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world did he go…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:29.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The same with Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:32.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How could they leave me behind…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:34.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“Guh?”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:40.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!\NWhat do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:44.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why, if it isn't the mysterious critter\Nfrom Ichigo's place…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mysterious critter?\NDon't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:51.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was just taking a walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:52.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:56.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to get a bit\Nof the night air!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:02.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You were left behind, felt lonely,\Nand chased after Ichigo, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:05.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-How could you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:07.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about Sister…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted to help her a little…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:17.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! I'm not finished talk…ing…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someone’s Spiritual Pressure\Njust increased!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:35.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he's fighting…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:38.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:47.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:50.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge…for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:53.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:20:00.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You need to recover your Quincy powers\Nin order to do that…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's a thorny path.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:10.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Bounts said earlier that\Nthey needed a Quincy's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:16.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And afterwards, they said that\Nthey had no need for a Quincy…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:17.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:21.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you think is true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:24.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:25.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:29.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ever think about\Nwhat would happen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:32.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,if you were able to recover\Nyour power?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:37.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I wasn't there,\Nshe might not have died…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Was that the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:46.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With your pride as a Quincy at stake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:49.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:52.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of tribe we are…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's young.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:01.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not bad at all…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:08.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You kid! You're all right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:10.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:11.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:16.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These guys really are targeting\Nthe souls of living humans…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:22.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll slice down every one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Master Kariya…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:26.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it…?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:30.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Soul Reaper is destroying the Bitto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How impertinent…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:40.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’ll soon learn what happens\Nwhen you damage a Bitto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:51.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you don't look like\Nyou have any wounds…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:53.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even hear me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.78,0:22:10.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:12.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:12.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:14.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:16.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,100 or 200…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:19.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:28.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sky blue dreams shine and flicker,\Ndancing away into the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:33.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The flowers glow and fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:49.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sky falls silent,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:55.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as a pair of\Ndreamy fireworks (Hanabi) lit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:23:02.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will sing my piercing love to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:07.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.26,0:23:12.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Blooming in an instant\Nare fireworks (Hanabi)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:19.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sky blue dreams shine and flicker,\Ndancing away into the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.72,0:23:23.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Blossom away in full bloom, high above
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:28.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Protect and keep those feelings thriving
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:35.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Strongly, at least till the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:42.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These flowers will glow and fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.57,0:23:57.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, Urahara said that\Nhe completed the tool to track Bounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.67,0:23:59.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!\NNow we'll know where they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.46,0:24:02.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He said he designed it\Nto match you perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.35,0:24:02.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Designed?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.96,0:24:03.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.47,0:24:05.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He said he can’t wait to\Nsee your surprised face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:07.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a really bad feeling\Nabout this…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:19.13,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Illustrated Guide to\NSoul Reapers after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.13,0:24:20.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.21,0:24:21.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.21,0:24:22.86,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,ASUDORA DRUGSTORE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.07,0:24:23.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much…!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.15,0:24:26.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my. Rangiku,\Nare you going on a trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.53,0:24:28.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going on a business trip\Nto the World of the Living!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.55,0:24:32.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The cosmetics there\Ndon't really match me…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.31,0:24:34.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Women always have\Na lot to pack at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.44,0:24:35.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you hate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.05,0:24:40.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I actually wanted to cut my hair\Na little before the trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.23,0:24:42.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but my captain is so noisy…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.89,0:24:45.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who's noisy…?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.00,0:24:46.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.13,0:24:48.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get going already!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.36,0:24:57.10,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me…